title: Rebecca Winters-Doorstep Twins
description:
Doorstep Twins
Rebecca Winters

   

Romantic Times Reviewers' Choice Award winner Rebecca Winters has been named the Utah Writer of the Year. In this captivating romantic tale, Gabi Turner travels to the Greek island of Milos to find Andreas, the father of her late sister's twin babies. Andreas Simonides is a powerful businessman who soon takes to caring for the twins and to Gabi herself. But he harbors a secret-the true identity of the children's father
